### Test League Score Calculation Service
### This file can be used with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3111/api
@authToken = YOUR_SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Test League Score Calculation (requires auth)
### This endpoint uses the authenticated user's Riot username from their profile
### Make sure your profile has a riot_username configured!
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/me/league-score
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test League Score Calculation with region parameter (default is europe)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/me/league-score?region=europe
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test League Score Calculation with different region (americas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/me/league-score?region=americas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

